data.description: Discover waterfront serenity in this 4-5 bed, 3 bath haven spanning 2286 sq ft. Immerse yourself in luxury with a residence graced by modern upgrades, ensuring a seamless blend of comfort and style. This expansive home invites you to relish the breathtaking waterfront views of Weiss Lake and moments from beautiful Yellow Creek falls, creating an idyllic backdrop for every moment. Seller is offering $ 5,000 dollars towards closing costs or a rate buy down. Don't wait on viewing this home before it is too late. Could be a great Airbnb or investment property also.
